name: TheAtlantic
text: Welcome to the great wait. Here's how to not go crazy the week before an election. The latest Atlantic Daily, by @mimbsy: https://t.co/UdWnF7abqR

name: TheAtlantic
text: RT @YAppelbaum: Jesse Helms’s hometown—like countrypolitan places across the country—is changing. And unless the GOP changes with it, it’s in big trouble. @GrahamDavidA reports from Union Country, North Carolina: https://t.co/ztUUQpXzLc

name: TheAtlantic
text: Countrypolitan places "are distinct from rural areas, which are mostly Republican, and cities, which are heavily Democratic ... That makes them pivotal counties, in 2020 and in the future," writes @GrahamDavidA: https://t.co/lgifxcuNRD
